Title: Extends provisions of law relating to big game hunting authorization for the county of Onondaga
Summary: Extends provisions of law relating to big game hunting authorization for the county of Onondaga until October 1, 2027.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend chapter 230 of the laws of 2023, amending the environmental conservation law relating to big game hunting authorization for the county of Onondaga, in relation to the effectiveness thereof
